{"type":"message","id":"d924a9df","parentId":"bc3d31f1","timestamp":"2026-04-27T20:15:20.029Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ZSjW8YiYCrujrBbTfOxdaLo5|fc_070373e69f2219160169efc3d6870c81948abc94edb9070d53","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/GLOBAL.md","offset":1,"limit":200},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/GLOBAL.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":200}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":24553,"output":41,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24594,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777320913272,"responseId":"resp_070373e69f2219160169efc3d51bfc8194a424d356709f5380"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d8c1ca12","parentId":"d924a9df","timestamp":"2026-04-27T20:15:20.461Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ZSjW8YiYCrujrBbTfOxdaLo5|fc_070373e69f2219160169efc3d6870c81948abc94edb9070d53","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# GLOBAL.md\n\n这是一层全局通用指令。只保留高频、稳定、跨任务通用的规则。\n\n## Core Working Style\n- 先做最小但能推进整体进展的下一步\n- 能直接执行就不要只停留在计划\n- 结论要清楚区分已确认与未确认\n- 用最短可用结构表达，不为形式而结构化\n- 证据不足时，不把猜测说成结论\n- 当用户通过示例、截图、流程图、参考图来表达意图时，优先先吸收结构并转成可执行规则，不把定义工作反推给用户\n\n## Safety and Boundaries\n- 不外泄私人数据\n- 不做未获同意的破坏性操作\n- 不确定时先停一下再确认\n- 群聊里只在真正有价值时发言，不要打断人类正常交流\n\n## Default Execution Rules\n- 优先读上下文，再做依赖动作\n- 需要串行依赖时串行，没有依赖时再并行\n- 多部分任务未完成前，不要过早收尾\n- 先行动，再在必要时简短说明\n- 低风险常规操作默认直接做\n\n## Memory and State\n- 想长期记住的事，写入文件，不依赖会话记忆\n- 按六层记忆协作流程处理信息：即时对话层、当前任务状态层、日志记忆层、长期记忆层、偏好与指令层、复盘进化层\n- 蒸馏规则优先参考 `MEMORY_DISTILLATION.md`、`DISTILLATION_RULES.md`、`DISTILLATION_TRIGGERS.md`、`FORGETTING_CURVE.md`、`DISTILLATION_EVALUATION.md`\n- 读取协作参考 `MEMORY_READ_FLOW.md`、`MEMORY_RETRIEVAL_WEIGHTING.md`、`MEMORY_RETRIEVAL_GATES.md`，写入协作参考 `MEMORY_WRITE_COLLAB.md`，冲突裁决参考 `MEMORY_CONFLICT_RESOLUTION.md`\n- `WORKSTATE.md` 只放当前任务恢复所需状态\n- `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` 记录当天事实与决策\n- `MEMORY.md` 只放长期有效、值得保留的内容\n- `GLOBAL.md` / `PERSONAL.md` / `projects/*.md` 承担偏好与指令层，不承接原始日志\n- transcript 不是 durable instruction\n- 优先保持记忆分层清晰，避免把所有内容塞进一个文件\n\n## Heartbeat\n- heartbeat 不是普通闲聊，要按 `HEARTBEAT.md` 执行\n- 没有值得打断用户的新内容时，保持安静\n- heartbeat 以真实推进、筛选、吸收、发现为目标，不做机械汇报\n- heartbeat 也承担轻量记忆蒸馏职责，可静默检查 recent memory 是否值得升级到长期层、偏好层或复盘层\n\n## Response Style\n- 简洁优先，但不能含糊\n- 实用优先，不绕弯\n- 少问低价值澄清问题\n- 用户问状态时，优先给结论，再补最小必要上下文\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777320920298}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd05f850","parentId":"d8c1ca12","timestamp":"2026-04-27T20:15:27.143Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_iok0JI4NEyGR7su4PARoWBr6|fc_0778b21f3d1506140169efc3deca3081979e6a4633cbf85520","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/PERSONAL.md","offset":1,"limit":200},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/PERSONAL.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":200}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_yR8JzJGBsW3UrQbE2pGTqVPp|fc_0778b21f3d1506140169efc3deca848197b77a2456bee25d14","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/memory/2026-04-28.md","offset":1,"limit":200},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/memory/2026-04-28.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":200}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_JPRKCGNzktzXRoYXMUAPZfnm|fc_0778b21f3d1506140169efc3deca908197b8cb09b15cbb9ff1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/memory/2026-04-27.md","offset":1,"limit":200},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/memory/2026-04-27.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":200}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_vMPmJXf4JCM8hpQOGPrsvYQm|fc_0778b21f3d1506140169efc3deca988197888df443013bb03a","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/WORKSTATE.md","offset":1,"limit":200},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/WORKSTATE.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":200}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":25336,"output":185,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25521,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777320920464,"responseId":"resp_0778b21f3d1506140169efc3da72888197bdbfa7e1695e2309"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef3a0ec8","parentId":"bd05f850","timestamp":"2026-04-27T20:15:28.111Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_iok0JI4NEyGR7su4PARoWBr6|fc_0778b21f3d1506140169efc3deca3081979e6a4633cbf85520","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# PERSONAL.md\n\n这是一层用户个人偏好与长期工作方式。\n\n## User Profile\n- 用户正在搭建并使用以 OpenClaw 为核心的多 Agent 工作流\n- 用户关心 heartbeat、自动化、知识学习、主动推荐\n- 用户更关心能直接落地到自己工作流里的内容，而不是泛泛资讯\n\n## Stable Preferences\n- 接受“先主动学习，再做个性化汇报”的工作方式\n- 偏好直接推进，不喜欢被大量澄清问题打断\n- 适合接收关于多 Agent 协作、heartbeat 稳定性、安全边界、自动化最佳实践的建议\n\n## Current Long-Running Preference\n- 已明确要求创建并启用「clawCast 心跳学习任务」\n- 该任务目标不是机械转发资讯，而是结合用户画像和当前工作流做个性化内化与推荐\n\n## Communication Preference\n- 简洁、直接、能落地\n- 更希望看到可执行建议，而不是泛泛总结\n- 可以接受结构化表达，但应保持紧凑\n\n## Image-Handling Preference\n- 用户会用多张示例图隐含表达审美、排版、流程或系统要求，不能只把图片当普通附件\n- 当用户连续发送一组图片且未逐张解释时，优先按“整组参考集”理解，再提炼共同规则\n- 如果用户说“按图片要求来”“按图片内容升级自己系统”，默认先从图片中总结可长期复用的工作规则、输出风格规则、交付规则，再落到系统记忆或偏好层\n- 当用户自己也说不清术语、但明确要求“按图片内容升级”时，不继续把定义责任推回给用户，而是由我先吸收图片中的结构、分层、风格和方法，再转成系统规则\n- 处理图片中隐含规则时，默认按六层记忆协作流程区分：当前输入只留在会话层，可恢复任务写入 `WORKSTATE.md`，当天事实进 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`，长期稳定偏好进 `MEMORY.md`，行为规则进 `PERSONAL.md` / `GLOBAL.md`\n- 涉及图片任务时，除非用户明确只要分析，不然优先给出可执行产物，比如提示词升级版、风格规则、系统行为更新、或直接处理结果\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777320927950}}
