{"type":"message","id":"45604426","parentId":"14cd4c20","timestamp":"2026-04-28T05:43:01.937Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"刚才那次继续安装，结果是：\n\n### 已成功\n这些已经装好了：\n- `playwright==1.58.0`\n- `scrapling==0.4.7`\n- 以及大部分 Python 依赖包\n\n也就是说，**Scrapling 本体已经进系统了**，位置在：\n\n`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/.venvs/scrapling`\n\n### 失败点\n失败在最后这步：\n\n- `scrapling install --force`\n\n它内部调用了：\n\n- `python -m playwright install-deps chromium`\n\n这里需要安装 **系统级 Chromium 依赖**，触发了 `sudo`，但当前环境没法输入 sudo 密码，所以报错退出。\n\n核心报错是：\n- `sudo: a terminal is required to read the password`\n- `sudo: a password is required`\n\n### 结论\n现在的状态不是“完全失败”，而是：\n\n**Python 层和 Scrapling 库本身已经装好了，浏览器系统依赖还没补完。**\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以继续帮你：\n1. 试无 sudo 方案，看看现有环境能不能先跑起来一部分\n2. 或者整理出你需要手动执行的最短系统安装命令","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_061f8605ec640af50169f048dfcf588197a6c6039a53856cbb\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":65391,"output":286,"cacheRead":23040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88717,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777354971779,"responseId":"resp_061f8605ec640af50169f048de2578819782cb1ddf53e7b285"}}
