{"type":"message","id":"2d229e0f","parentId":"32429bf7","timestamp":"2026-04-28T06:33:56.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"支持，而且我刚已经替你验证过了，**本机能装、也能跑**。\n\n### 结果\n`crawl4ai` 现在已经成功装到本机虚拟环境里：\n\n- 路径：`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/.venvs/crawl4ai`\n\n### 我实际验证了什么\n我没有只停在安装成功，而是做了实际抓取测试：\n\n- 用 `crawl4ai` 抓了 `https://example.com`\n- 成功完成了：\n  - INIT\n  - FETCH\n  - SCRAPE\n  - COMPLETE\n\n### 实际输出\n抓到的 markdown 是：\n\n- `# Example Domain`\n- `This domain is for use in documentation examples without needing permission.`\n- `Learn more`\n\n### 结论\n**支持安装到本机，而且现在已经可用了。**\n\n一句话对比：\n\n- **Scrapling**：也装上了，基础抓取已可用，但抓微信公众号时被微信风控拦了\n- **crawl4ai**：本机也能装，而且最小抓取验证已跑通\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以直接：\n1. **拿 crawl4ai 去抓你刚才那篇公众号**\n2. **顺手比较 Scrapling 和 crawl4ai 对微信文章哪个更稳**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_061f8605ec640af50169f054cd9610819798cb5547497cc024\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":103276,"output":294,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777358025887,"responseId":"resp_061f8605ec640af50169f054cba0dc8197b7cc015c27d72233"}}
