{"type":"message","id":"7df73015","parentId":"0bd1117d","timestamp":"2026-04-28T06:35:10.735Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我直接拿 crawl4ai 去试抓这篇公众号。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_061f8605ec640af50169f0551ca3c881979cb05ce946879695\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_urwI9FvQASWGzbhL9v2sNfMZ|fc_061f8605ec640af50169f0551d20fc8197b44809da1f85b9c2","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","bracketed":false,"data":"","eof":false,"hex":[],"keys":[],"limit":4000,"literal":"","offset":0,"sessionId":"rapid-nudibranch","text":"","timeout":1800000},"partialJson":"{\"action\":\"poll\",\"bracketed\":false,\"data\":\"\",\"eof\":false,\"hex\":[],\"keys\":[],\"limit\":4000,\"literal\":\"\",\"offset\":0,\"sessionId\":\"rapid-nudibranch\",\"text\":\"\",\"timeout\":1800000}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2450,"output":84,"cacheRead":102400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104934,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777358103818,"responseId":"resp_061f8605ec640af50169f0551996b081979b729e726ee234ed"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9484aa01","parentId":"7df73015","timestamp":"2026-04-28T06:35:15.400Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_urwI9FvQASWGzbhL9v2sNfMZ|fc_061f8605ec640af50169f0551d20fc8197b44809da1f85b9c2","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[INIT].... → Crawl4AI 0.8.6 \n[FETCH]... ↓ https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nLdz70HxiuO7AfmIRQqMqA                  \n| ✓ | ⏱: 2.78s \n[SCRAPE].. ◆ https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nLdz70HxiuO7AfmIRQqMqA                  \n| ✓ | ⏱: 0.01s \n[COMPLETE] ● https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nLdz70HxiuO7AfmIRQqMqA                  \n| ✓ | ⏱: 2.80s \nSUCCESS True\nSTATUS 302\nURL https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nLdz70HxiuO7AfmIRQqMqA\nERROR \n\n---OUT---\n## 环境异常\n当前环境异常，完成验证后即可继续访问。\n去验证\n:  ， . Video Mini Program Like ，轻点两下取消赞 Wow ，轻点两下取消在看\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"rapid-nudibranch","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[INIT].... → Crawl4AI 0.8.6 \n[FETCH]... ↓ https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nLdz70HxiuO7AfmIRQqMqA                  \n| ✓ | ⏱: 2.78s \n[SCRAPE].. ◆ https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nLdz70HxiuO7AfmIRQqMqA                  \n| ✓ | ⏱: 0.01s \n[COMPLETE] ● https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nLdz70HxiuO7AfmIRQqMqA                  \n| ✓ | ⏱: 2.80s \nSUCCESS True\nSTATUS 302\nURL https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nLdz70HxiuO7AfmIRQqMqA\nERROR \n\n---OUT---\n## 环境异常\n当前环境异常，完成验证后即可继续访问。\n去验证\n:  ， . Video Mini Program Like ，轻点两下取消赞 Wow ，轻点两下取消在看\n","name":"set VENV=/vol1/@apphome/tr...kspace/.venvs/crawl4ai"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777358115294}}
{"type":"message","id":"5ce06ece","parentId":"9484aa01","timestamp":"2026-04-28T06:35:41.803Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"试了，结果和 Scrapling 很接近：\n\n### crawl4ai 实测结果\n- 抓取流程本身成功\n- 但拿到的不是正文，而是微信验证页\n\n### 抓到的内容\n主要是：\n\n- `环境异常`\n- `当前环境异常，完成验证后即可继续访问。`\n- `去验证`\n\n### 关键状态\n- `SUCCESS: True`\n- `STATUS: 302`\n\n这说明：\n**crawl4ai 也成功访问到了页面流程，但被微信跳转到了验证页。**\n\n### 结论\n这篇公众号文章目前的问题不是：\n- Scrapling 不行\n- crawl4ai 不行\n\n而是：\n\n**微信对当前抓取环境统一触发了风控验证。**\n\n### 现在的真实判断\n对这篇链接来说：\n\n- **Scrapling**：被拦到验证页\n- **crawl4ai**：也被拦到验证页\n\n所以瓶颈不在库，而在 **微信风控**。\n\n### 下一步最靠谱的路\n如果你真要拿正文，我建议走这两种之一：\n\n1. **接入真实浏览器登录态**\n   - 用你自己的浏览器上下文\n   - 成功率最高\n\n2. **换别的内容源**\n   - 如果这篇文章有转载页、镜像页、摘要页，往往更容易拿正文\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以继续帮你：\n- **试用当前宿主浏览器上下文抓这篇微信文章**\n- 或者 **帮你找这篇文章在别处的可抓版本**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_061f8605ec640af50169f05536e95c8197a27992cab87b501d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":13518,"output":354,"cacheRead":91648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105520,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777358115407,"responseId":"resp_061f8605ec640af50169f05525bfb48197885fddc6eebb1111"}}
