{"type":"message","id":"84cdde6c","parentId":"bdaba65b","timestamp":"2026-04-28T06:35:49.638Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-04-28 14:35:15 GMT+8] Exec completed (rapid-nu, code 0) :: | ✓ | ⏱: 2.78s [SCRAPE].. ◆ https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nLdz70HxiuO7AfmIRQqMqA | ✓ | ⏱: 0.01s [COMPLETE] ● https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nLdz70HxiuO7AfmIRQqMqA | ✓ | ⏱: 2.80s SUCCESS …\n\nAn async command you ran earlier has completed. The result is shown in the system messages above. Please relay the command output to the user in a helpful way. If the command succeeded, share the relevant output. If it failed, explain what went wrong.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 28th, 2026 - 2:35 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-28 06:35 UTC"}],"timestamp":1777358149528}}
{"type":"message","id":"74c60dd3","parentId":"84cdde6c","timestamp":"2026-04-28T06:35:59.530Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"刚才这次 `crawl4ai` 命令本身是成功的，但结果说明它也被微信风控拦住了。\n\n### 实测结果\n- Crawl4AI 流程跑通了：\n  - `INIT`\n  - `FETCH`\n  - `SCRAPE`\n  - `COMPLETE`\n- 返回状态里显示：\n  - `SUCCESS True`\n  - `STATUS 302`\n\n### 抓到的实际内容\n保存下来的正文不是文章内容，而是微信验证页，核心内容是：\n\n- `环境异常`\n- `当前环境异常，完成验证后即可继续访问。`\n- `去验证`\n\n### 结论\n这说明：\n\n**crawl4ai 已经成功访问到这个链接流程，但微信把它重定向到了验证页，而不是正文页。**\n\n所以现在的判断很明确：\n- 不是工具没装好\n- 不是 crawl4ai 不会抓\n- 是 **微信风控把当前抓取环境拦下来了**\n\n### 综合判断\n对这篇公众号文章来说：\n\n- Scrapling 会被拦\n- Crawl4AI 也会被拦\n\n因此瓶颈不在抓取库，而在 **微信验证机制**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_061f8605ec640af50169f0554a491081979dbc9e449def813a\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":82636,"output":265,"cacheRead":23040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105941,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777358149638,"responseId":"resp_061f8605ec640af50169f055474c908197b06f039c1c5a31ed"}}
