{"type":"message","id":"84dfc05e","parentId":"9fa3087e","timestamp":"2026-04-28T08:18:18.836Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"刚才那步我已经替你收完了，结论是：\n\n### 已成功的部分\n- `camofox-browser` 仓库已经拉到本地\n- `npm install` 已跑完\n- `node_modules` 已存在\n- 项目本身的 Node 依赖已经装好\n\n本地路径是：\n\n`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/tools/camofox-browser`\n\n### 失败的部分\n失败在它的 `postinstall` 下载阶段。\n\n它会自动执行：\n\n- `npx camoufox-js fetch`\n\n然后去下载 Camoufox 运行时和附加资源，但下载过程中网络超时/重置了，具体表现是：\n\n- `api.github.com` 访问失败\n- `addons.mozilla.org` 下载失败\n- 最后报：\n  - `Failed to download from https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/downloads/latest/ublock-origin/latest.xpi after 5 attempts`\n\n### 这意味着什么\n所以当前状态不是“完全没装上”，而是：\n\n**源码和 npm 依赖装好了，但 Camoufox 浏览器资源没拉完整。**\n\n也就是：\n- 项目目录在\n- 依赖在\n- 运行时资源不完整\n- 暂时不能算 fully ready\n\n### 一句话\n**现在是半安装成功，卡在外部资源下载，不是代码本体安装失败。**\n\n如果你要继续，我建议下一步优先改走 **Docker 安装**，这个项目本来就对 Docker 支持更自然。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_061f8605ec640af50169f06d4431d48197a68d7d4abc74df05\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":116404,"output":340,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116744,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777364288085,"responseId":"resp_061f8605ec640af50169f06d426d348197abccd9c9083a5647"}}
